      "rationale": "All three ensemble models employ nonlinear large-deformation formulations with Ti-6Al-4V elasto-plastic material law (bilinear isotropic hardening, yield stress 880 MPa). Frictional contact (mu=0.2) modeled at all interfaces. Ensemble spread across three independently constructed models provides empirical model-form uncertainty estimate. Gradation 3 achieved."
