      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties (E=114 GPa, sigma_y=880 MPa, n=0.05) derived from tensile coupon testing of the same production lot as test constructs. Geometric dimensions verified by CMM with <0.01 mm tolerance. LHS uncertainty propagation (n=200 samples) quantifies input parameter contribution to total validation uncertainty. Gradation 3 achieved."
