      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production hardware by trained spine surgery team following clinical assembly protocol. All constructs dimensionally inspected; screw-rod interface torque recorded. Constructs span two independent laboratories to capture inter-lab variability. Gradation 3 satisfied."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
