      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties, geometry, boundary conditions, and loading in FEA match experimental test conditions within documented tolerances; traceability matrix provided.",
      "rationale": "Traceability matrix maps each experimental parameter (screw geometry, rod diameter, UHMWPE block geometry, loading fixture, applied displacement) to corresponding FEA input. All parameters matched within measurement uncertainty. Screw-rod torque applied in FEA matches experimental assembly torque (4 Nm ± 0.2 Nm). Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
