      "rationale": "Pre-specified acceptance bounds (<10% QoI difference, E/uval <1.96) documented in analysis plan prior to unblinding. All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) for all three ensemble members satisfy both criteria. Maximum percent difference 7.3% (FDA model, yield force); maximum E/uval 1.41 (Ansys model, force at 40 mm). Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
