      "rationale": "Validation constructs use production non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws identical to those in the COU submission. ASTM F1717 test protocol is the regulatory standard for this device class. Two-laboratory design ensures validation domain encompasses inter-facility variability. COU is the ASTM F1717 submission itself, so validation and use domains are coincident. Gradation 3 achieved."
