    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "12 of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required level. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) reflects the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol; this limitation is acknowledged and accepted given that ASTM F1717 is the regulatory standard for this device class and the remaining 12 factors provide sufficient overall credibility for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence COU. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
